description: Cyclone Blakk Widow Flavored Pre Rolled Paper Cones are cool New cones that have the added bonus of having the great taste of fresh Widow. All Cyclone cones are pre-rolled with a roach, meaning you have no fuss or mess and allows you to spend less time rolling and more time enjoy your tasty smoke. The cone is packaged in a handy hard tube that can be used to snuff out your cigarette so you can save it to enjoy later. The tube also makes sure that the cone stays in tip-top condition and is always fresh and full of flavor. Each tube contains: 2 Blakk Widow Cones and 1 re-useable red wooden tip.
